1
00:00:09,468 --> 00:00:10,828
<font color=#FFFF00>I am an adoptee.</font>

2
00:00:12,268 --> 00:00:13,798
<font color=#FFFF00>An adoptee from an orphanage.</font>

3
00:00:17,528 --> 00:00:19,328
<font color=#FFFF00>And a brother who's looking for his younger brother...</font>

4
00:00:20,028 --> 00:00:21,598
<font color=#FFFF00>whom he lost 20 years ago.</font>

5
00:00:24,068 --> 00:00:25,328
<font color=#FFFF00>That's who I am.</font>

6
00:00:27,728 --> 00:00:29,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

7
00:00:30,628 --> 00:00:31,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

8
00:00:32,298 --> 00:00:33,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you feel better now?</font>

9
00:00:37,598 --> 00:00:38,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

10
00:00:39,428 --> 00:00:41,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know.</font>

11
00:00:41,568 --> 00:00:44,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know you had such a painful past.</font>

12
00:00:44,768 --> 00:00:46,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry for being so immature.</font>

13
00:00:49,768 --> 00:00:51,798
<font color=#FFFF00>After 20 years have passed,</font>

14
00:00:53,268 --> 00:00:54,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

15
00:00:55,898 --> 00:00:57,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I can find my brother now.</font>

16
00:00:58,928 --> 00:00:59,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Excuse me?</font>

17
00:01:00,928 --> 00:01:01,938
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

18
00:01:03,028 --> 00:01:04,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I can find my bother now.</font>

19
00:01:06,898 --> 00:01:07,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

20
00:01:11,868 --> 00:01:14,868
<font color=#FFFF00>So please trust me and wait a little.</font>

21
00:01:15,628 --> 00:01:18,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I will never make you sad...</font>

22
00:01:19,098 --> 00:01:20,098
<font color=#FFFF00>or hurt you again.</font>

23
00:01:22,298 --> 00:01:24,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Please bear with me...</font>

24
00:01:25,668 --> 00:01:26,768
<font color=#FFFF00>until I find my brother.</font>

25
00:01:36,198 --> 00:01:37,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

26
00:01:38,698 --> 00:01:39,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I will wait.</font>

27
00:01:40,428 --> 00:01:41,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I will bear with you.</font>

28
00:01:43,228 --> 00:01:44,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Also,</font>

29
00:01:45,998 --> 00:01:47,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I will trust you.</font>

30
00:01:53,298 --> 00:01:55,298
<font color=#FFFF00>You're no longer the wild girl I used to know.</font>

31
00:01:56,368 --> 00:01:58,628
<font color=#FFFF00>The neighborhood will thank me for it.</font>

32
00:02:02,098 --> 00:02:03,198
<font color=#FFFF00>You made it happen.</font>

33
00:02:11,998 --> 00:02:13,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang.</font>

34
00:02:16,428 --> 00:02:18,198
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you two doing right now?</font>

35
00:02:19,928 --> 00:02:21,068
<font color=#FFFF00>What brings you all the way here?</font>

36
00:02:21,468 --> 00:02:23,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, I mean Director Han.</font>

37
00:02:24,368 --> 00:02:26,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know what's happening at the company?</font>

38
00:02:26,968 --> 00:02:30,068
<font color=#FFFF00>How can the director be out of reach?</font>

39
00:02:31,868 --> 00:02:33,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry. I left my phone downstairs.</font>

40
00:02:34,428 --> 00:02:35,498
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

41
00:02:35,628 --> 00:02:37,298
<font color=#FFFF00>You two are unbelievable.</font>

42
00:02:38,598 --> 00:02:39,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang.</font>

43
00:02:39,768 --> 00:02:41,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Jo won't work with us.</font>

44
00:02:42,168 --> 00:02:43,198
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

45
00:02:45,598 --> 00:02:47,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know who she is?</font>

46
00:02:47,198 --> 00:02:49,398
<font color=#FFFF00>She's the girl who came the other time.</font>

47
00:02:49,428 --> 00:02:50,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is that?</font>

48
00:02:50,798 --> 00:02:53,268
<font color=#FFFF00>She's Seong Joon's fiance.</font>

49
00:02:55,168 --> 00:02:56,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

50
00:02:56,368 --> 00:02:58,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon said she is not his fiance.</font>

51
00:02:59,398 --> 00:03:00,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey!</font>

52
00:03:01,028 --> 00:03:02,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey!</font>

53
00:03:02,368 --> 00:03:03,868
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the reason?</font>

54
00:03:03,928 --> 00:03:06,268
<font color=#FFFF00>There's a problem with her previous employee.</font>

55
00:03:06,528 --> 00:03:07,828
<font color=#FFFF00>She's contracted to write 10 more episodes for them,</font>

56
00:03:07,828 --> 00:03:10,728
<font color=#FFFF00>so we were going to return them the money for those manuscripts.</font>

57
00:03:10,898 --> 00:03:13,928
<font color=#FFFF00>But they claimed the priority right and decided to resign with her.</font>

58
00:03:14,428 --> 00:03:15,528
<font color=#FFFF00>No way.</font>

59
00:03:15,668 --> 00:03:17,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Writer Jo right now?</font>

60
00:03:17,528 --> 00:03:20,268
<font color=#FFFF00>She's at the writing room. Her agent is coming too.</font>

61
00:03:20,498 --> 00:03:22,268
<font color=#FFFF00>We're going to have a meeting there.</font>

62
00:03:22,698 --> 00:03:25,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Hurry up and get ready, Seong Joon. You don't have time to play house.</font>

63
00:03:40,428 --> 00:03:41,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

64
00:03:41,598 --> 00:03:42,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is she?</font>

65
00:03:43,598 --> 00:03:46,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, I have to go to the office. There's an emergency.</font>

66
00:03:47,328 --> 00:03:48,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

67
00:03:49,998 --> 00:03:51,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon. Seong Joon.</font>

68
00:03:55,468 --> 00:03:57,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm in a hurry, but I have to ask you a question.</font>

69
00:03:58,398 --> 00:03:59,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Director.</font>

70
00:03:59,998 --> 00:04:01,698
<font color=#FFFF00>What were you two doing?</font>

71
00:04:02,568 --> 00:04:04,498
<font color=#FFFF00>We were studying the script.</font>

72
00:04:05,468 --> 00:04:06,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say you were studying the script?</font>

73
00:04:07,098 --> 00:04:08,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

74
00:04:09,098 --> 00:04:10,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui,</font>

75
00:04:10,498 --> 00:04:13,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I shouldn't meddle with the family...</font>

76
00:04:13,168 --> 00:04:15,298
<font color=#FFFF00>getting along so well,</font>

77
00:04:15,398 --> 00:04:17,568
<font color=#FFFF00>but I hope you will not get carried away by something personal...</font>

78
00:04:17,568 --> 00:04:20,728
<font color=#FFFF00>like this and let it affect your work again.</font>

79
00:04:21,468 --> 00:04:22,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

80
00:04:26,028 --> 00:04:27,298
<font color=#FFFF00>You're here.</font>

81
00:04:28,098 --> 00:04:29,668
<font color=#FFFF00>My guess was right.</font>

82
00:04:29,868 --> 00:04:31,528
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew it was you.</font>

83
00:04:31,928 --> 00:04:34,228
<font color=#FFFF00>We have an emergency at work,</font>

84
00:04:34,298 --> 00:04:37,568
<font color=#FFFF00>and Seong Joon wasn't picking up his phone.</font>

85
00:04:37,728 --> 00:04:40,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Did something bad happen at work?</font>

86
00:04:40,138 --> 00:04:42,198
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's nothing bad.</font>

87
00:04:42,368 --> 00:04:44,668
<font color=#FFFF00>It just needs to be addressed right away. That's all.</font>

88
00:04:44,968 --> 00:04:48,698
<font color=#FFFF00>It turned out he left his phone downstairs.</font>

89
00:04:49,168 --> 00:04:50,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Only if Seong Joon...</font>

90
00:04:51,228 --> 00:04:52,398
<font color=#FFFF00>had his phone,</font>

91
00:04:52,968 --> 00:04:56,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I wouldn't have ruined your holiday.</font>

92
00:04:56,198 --> 00:04:57,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

93
00:04:57,698 --> 00:05:00,428
<font color=#FFFF00>You were just doing your work. I understand.</font>

94
00:05:00,898 --> 00:05:03,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I will get going now then.</font>

95
00:05:03,198 --> 00:05:05,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon must be waiting for me downstairs.</font>

96
00:05:05,268 --> 00:05:06,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. Go ahead.</font>

97
00:05:07,198 --> 00:05:08,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll visit you again next time.</font>

98
00:05:08,768 --> 00:05:10,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. Take care.</font>

99
00:05:18,298 --> 00:05:20,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, do you have time?</font>

100
00:05:22,028 --> 00:05:23,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I do.</font>

101
00:05:23,798 --> 00:05:26,168
<font color=#FFFF00>If I knew they were going to leave so soon,</font>

102
00:05:26,628 --> 00:05:29,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I wouldn't have brought up tea.</font>

103
00:05:30,798 --> 00:05:33,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Since I brought up two cups of tea, we should drink it together.</font>

104
00:05:34,368 --> 00:05:35,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure.</font>

105
00:05:42,468 --> 00:05:45,228
<font color=#FFFF00>It's decorated quite well here.</font>

106
00:05:45,598 --> 00:05:48,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. Seong Hoon helped us a lot.</font>

107
00:05:49,128 --> 00:05:50,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I see. Seong Hoon...</font>

108
00:05:50,828 --> 00:05:53,068
<font color=#FFFF00>cares a lot about his in-laws.</font>

109
00:05:55,898 --> 00:05:58,368
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, you are always busy writing.</font>

110
00:05:58,898 --> 00:06:00,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you want to get married?</font>

111
00:06:01,528 --> 00:06:02,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Do I want to get married?</font>

112
00:06:02,998 --> 00:06:04,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

113
00:06:05,998 --> 00:06:08,498
<font color=#FFFF00>You are quite old now.</font>

114
00:06:09,628 --> 00:06:11,328
<font color=#FFFF00>It's time to think about settling down with someone, you know?</font>

115
00:06:12,168 --> 00:06:13,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know. I haven't thought about it yet.</font>

116
00:06:14,498 --> 00:06:16,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I've already married off my two sons,</font>

117
00:06:16,798 --> 00:06:18,768
<font color=#FFFF00>and now there's only Seong Joon left.</font>

118
00:06:20,598 --> 00:06:21,968
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why...</font>

119
00:06:22,768 --> 00:06:24,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I want Seong Joon...</font>

120
00:06:24,728 --> 00:06:27,028
<font color=#FFFF00>to marry better person than...</font>

121
00:06:27,398 --> 00:06:29,298
<font color=#FFFF00>his brothers.</font>

122
00:06:31,298 --> 00:06:33,468
<font color=#FFFF00>That's how mothers feel, you know?</font>

123
00:06:34,198 --> 00:06:37,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Rather than marrying a poor girl who is kind,</font>

124
00:06:37,168 --> 00:06:39,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I want him to marry a wealthy and educated girl...</font>

125
00:06:40,098 --> 00:06:43,728
<font color=#FFFF00>who was brought up with much love.</font>

126
00:06:43,928 --> 00:06:46,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I want that kind of a girl to be my daughter-in-law.</font>

127
00:06:47,098 --> 00:06:50,368
<font color=#FFFF00>That will make his marriage life easier too.</font>

128
00:06:52,698 --> 00:06:53,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course.</font>

129
00:06:54,198 --> 00:06:55,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure...</font>

130
00:06:55,968 --> 00:06:57,328
<font color=#FFFF00>you are a clever girl.</font>

131
00:06:58,098 --> 00:07:00,628
<font color=#FFFF00>You're a writer too, so I'm sure you understand...</font>

132
00:07:00,628 --> 00:07:02,368
<font color=#FFFF00>mother's feelings well.</font>

133
00:07:05,268 --> 00:07:06,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

134
00:07:08,568 --> 00:07:11,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you marry well too.</font>

135
00:07:24,068 --> 00:07:26,268
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't say anything strange...</font>

136
00:07:26,498 --> 00:07:28,468
<font color=#FFFF00>to that girl, did you?</font>

137
00:07:28,898 --> 00:07:31,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't get to talk to her.</font>

138
00:07:31,668 --> 00:07:34,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Something came up at the office, so they rushed off.</font>

139
00:07:35,468 --> 00:07:36,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Instead,</font>

140
00:07:37,728 --> 00:07:39,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I had some tea with Dong Hui.</font>

141
00:07:40,698 --> 00:07:42,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you have tea with Dong Hui?</font>

142
00:07:42,198 --> 00:07:43,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I just warned her a little.</font>

143
00:07:44,368 --> 00:07:45,728
<font color=#FFFF00>What is there to warn her about?</font>

144
00:07:47,128 --> 00:07:48,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh...</font>

145
00:07:49,198 --> 00:07:51,828
<font color=#FFFF00>educated her children so well.</font>

146
00:07:52,168 --> 00:07:54,128
<font color=#FFFF00>She's flawless.</font>

147
00:07:54,268 --> 00:07:56,398
<font color=#FFFF00>She is hardly flawless.</font>

148
00:07:56,398 --> 00:07:59,628
<font color=#FFFF00>She spends all day with Seong Joon in that small space.</font>

149
00:07:59,668 --> 00:08:01,768
<font color=#FFFF00>They don't even come out for hours.</font>

150
00:08:01,768 --> 00:08:04,068
<font color=#FFFF00>So how can I not warn her?</font>

151
00:08:04,728 --> 00:08:08,328
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you imagining?</font>

152
00:08:08,528 --> 00:08:11,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I smell something fishy.</font>

153
00:08:12,198 --> 00:08:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I think there's something going on between them.</font>

154
00:08:15,028 --> 00:08:18,368
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey. - You don't know anything.</font>

155
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:21,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Young people are different.</font>

156
00:08:21,968 --> 00:08:24,668
<font color=#FFFF00>They don't care if they are in-laws.</font>

157
00:08:24,668 --> 00:08:26,398
<font color=#FFFF00>You are unbelievable.</font>

158
00:08:26,468 --> 00:08:28,298
<font color=#FFFF00>And you know Seong Joon.</font>

159
00:08:28,298 --> 00:08:31,898
<font color=#FFFF00>He's just like you. He has a soft spot for the weak.</font>

160
00:08:31,968 --> 00:08:34,398
<font color=#FFFF00>So you're saying Seong Joon...</font>

161
00:08:34,498 --> 00:08:37,238
<font color=#FFFF00>likes her. Is that what you're saying?</font>

162
00:08:37,298 --> 00:08:40,238
<font color=#FFFF00>That can't happen. They are in-laws for crying out loud.</font>

163
00:08:40,398 --> 00:08:42,868
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I am taking precautionary measures.</font>

164
00:08:44,268 --> 00:08:46,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, you should...</font>

165
00:08:47,168 --> 00:08:48,738
<font color=#FFFF00>warn Seong Joon too.</font>

166
00:08:49,328 --> 00:08:50,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it.</font>

167
00:09:14,368 --> 00:09:16,098
<font color=#FFFF00>We lost her after all.</font>

168
00:09:16,568 --> 00:09:19,238
<font color=#FFFF00>I haven't had the faintest idea that this could happen.</font>

169
00:09:19,828 --> 00:09:24,068
<font color=#FFFF00>How can they sign 10 more episodes? Their contract already ended.</font>

170
00:09:24,568 --> 00:09:27,568
<font color=#FFFF00>She came to us first because she took care of it.</font>

171
00:09:29,628 --> 00:09:31,268
<font color=#FFFF00>This is how businesses in this field run.</font>

172
00:09:31,768 --> 00:09:34,168
<font color=#FFFF00>We only have us to blame. We should have been more careful.</font>

173
00:09:34,328 --> 00:09:36,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I will try my best to...</font>

174
00:09:36,098 --> 00:09:38,498
<font color=#FFFF00>avoid cancellation of the air time we already acquired.</font>

175
00:09:39,028 --> 00:09:42,568
<font color=#FFFF00>However, we must find her replacement right away.</font>

176
00:09:46,998 --> 00:09:49,768
<font color=#FFFF00>What is the agenda of the meeting of the shareholders?</font>

177
00:09:50,298 --> 00:09:53,238
<font color=#FFFF00>The biggest agenda is regarding...</font>

178
00:09:53,328 --> 00:09:55,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Contents and Marketing Department's performance.</font>

179
00:09:55,768 --> 00:09:57,928
<font color=#FFFF00>My gosh. How idiotic.</font>

180
00:09:58,428 --> 00:10:01,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I shouldn't have put them in charge in the first place.</font>

181
00:10:01,868 --> 00:10:03,128
<font color=#FFFF00>They are still young.</font>

182
00:10:04,198 --> 00:10:07,368
<font color=#FFFF00>- What else? - The more important agenda is...</font>

183
00:10:07,868 --> 00:10:11,028
<font color=#FFFF00>the disappearance of the former president, Park Chang Wook.</font>

184
00:10:12,828 --> 00:10:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>They are so brutal.</font>

185
00:10:15,628 --> 00:10:19,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are they so anxious to declare his death?</font>

186
00:10:21,768 --> 00:10:22,768
<font color=#FFFF00>And...</font>

187
00:10:23,738 --> 00:10:25,098
<font color=#FFFF00>how many are on my side?</font>

188
00:10:25,568 --> 00:10:26,928
<font color=#FFFF00>It's more than majority,</font>

189
00:10:27,568 --> 00:10:30,098
<font color=#FFFF00>but the opposing side is requesting...</font>

190
00:10:30,668 --> 00:10:32,628
<font color=#FFFF00>to disclose the president's will.</font>

191
00:10:34,498 --> 00:10:37,238
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness. Nothing is going my way.</font>

192
00:10:39,828 --> 00:10:42,098
<font color=#FFFF00>- Okay. You can go now. - Yes, Sir.</font>

193
00:10:47,498 --> 00:10:50,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard the contract with Writer Jo was nullified.</font>

194
00:10:51,398 --> 00:10:53,598
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you find out?</font>

195
00:10:53,798 --> 00:10:55,268
<font color=#FFFF00>It just happened this morning.</font>

196
00:10:55,768 --> 00:10:58,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Since you are looking down on me,</font>

197
00:10:58,928 --> 00:11:01,328
<font color=#FFFF00>that is why Director Han is...</font>

198
00:11:02,428 --> 00:11:04,068
<font color=#FFFF00>not afraid of me.</font>

199
00:11:04,928 --> 00:11:08,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm glad it happened. The shareholders didn't like...</font>

200
00:11:08,228 --> 00:11:10,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han and Contents Department.</font>

201
00:11:11,428 --> 00:11:13,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Now you can disband the team.</font>

202
00:11:13,498 --> 00:11:15,868
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad, I can't do that. - And...</font>

203
00:11:16,068 --> 00:11:18,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Fire Han Seong Joon now.</font>

204
00:11:18,798 --> 00:11:20,698
<font color=#FFFF00>This is when you accept his resignation letter.</font>

205
00:11:21,228 --> 00:11:24,568
<font color=#FFFF00>We are not supposed to fooled by him like the previous time.</font>

206
00:11:24,628 --> 00:11:26,628
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad. - It's the end of our conversation.</font>

207
00:11:27,668 --> 00:11:30,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad, give me some time to regroup.</font>

208
00:11:30,428 --> 00:11:32,498
<font color=#FFFF00>We can manage this crisis. please?</font>

209
