00:17:20,938 --> 00:17:24,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm throwing a party at home. So please come home early.</font>

275
00:17:26,798 --> 00:17:30,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. I'm so proud of you, Chang Soo.</font>

276
00:17:30,628 --> 00:17:31,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

277
00:17:31,798 --> 00:17:35,128
<font color=#FFFF00>- How do you feel, Ms. Oh? - I feel so happy.</font>

278
00:17:35,328 --> 00:17:39,128
<font color=#FFFF00>I had no idea that Chang Soo would have a talent like that.</font>

279
00:17:39,128 --> 00:17:43,098
