342
00:20:47,828 --> 00:20:50,598
<font color=#FFFF00>because of Hee Sook.</font>

343
00:20:50,598 --> 00:20:52,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, I've been the same too.</font>

344
00:20:52,828 --> 00:20:53,938
