<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook isn't the only drama queen, but you are too.</font>

413
00:25:22,798 --> 00:25:25,468
<font color=#FFFF00>You two are no different from each other.</font>

414
00:25:25,768 --> 00:25:28,668
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not what I meant. I asked it for a reason.</font>

415
00:25:28,928 --> 00:25:30,168
<font color=#FFFF00>For a reason?</font>

416
00:25:30,168 --> 00:25:31,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it already.</font>

417
00:25:32,328 --> 00:25:34,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you yelling at me? Why?</font>

418
00:25:38,428 --> 00:25:39,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandma.</font>

419
00:25:40,598 --> 00:25:42,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Dong Hui.</font>

420
00:25:43,498 --> 00:25:45,868
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing here? It's cold outside.</font>

421
00:25:47,268 --> 00:25:48,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Well,</font>

422
00:25:48,898 --> 00:25:51,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I just thought you'd be writing.</font>

423
00:25:52,068 --> 00:25:54,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come inside. It's cold here.</font>

424
00:25:55,998 --> 00:25:58,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. Let's go in.</font>

425
00:26:03,468 --> 00:26:05,928
<font color=#FFFF00>- Please drink some tea. - Okay.</font>

426
00:26:06,398 --> 00:26:07,968
<font color=#FFFF00>How is your arm?</font>

427
00:26:08,398 --> 00:26:10,698
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it will take a while to recover...</font>

428
00:26:10,728 --> 00:26:12,468
<font color=#FFFF00>since I'm old.</font>

429
00:26:12,798 --> 00:26:15,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you take the cleaning job? You don't have to work.</font>

430
00:26:16,628 --> 00:26:19,868
<font color=#FFFF00>If I don't, how am I going to help you when you get married?</font>

431
00:26:20,668 --> 00:26:21,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandma,</font>

432
00:26:22,198 --> 00:26:23,668
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not going to marry.</font>

433
00:26:24,398 --> 00:26:25,998
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you talking about?</font>

434
00:26:26,928 --> 00:26:28,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to live with you like now.</font>

435
00:26:29,068 --> 00:26:32,028
<font color=#FFFF00>You know I can't live forever.</font>

436
00:26:32,598 --> 00:26:34,898
<font color=#FFFF00>My scenario will be dramatized soon.</font>

437
00:26:34,998 --> 00:26:38,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I might become a sought-after writer when it's aired.</font>

438
00:26:39,168 --> 00:26:41,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I will just keep writing...</font>

439
00:26:41,168 --> 00:26:43,498
<font color=#FFFF00>and live happily with you, Grandma.</font>

440
00:26:50,568 --> 00:26:51,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you...</font>

441
00:26:52,628 --> 00:26:54,928
<font color=#FFFF00>have a boyfriend?</font>

442
00:26:55,768 --> 00:26:58,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry? No, I don't.</font>

443
00:26:59,628 --> 00:27:00,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Then,</font>

444
00:27:01,968 --> 00:27:04,168
<font color=#FFFF00>do you have any man...</font>

445
00:27:04,728 --> 00:27:05,798
<font color=#FFFF00>of your heart?</font>

446
00:27:07,428 --> 00:27:09,668
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't. Why are you asking such things?</font>

447
00:27:11,868 --> 00:27:13,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel sorry for you.</font>

448
00:27:15,198 --> 00:27:17,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I couldn't send you to a college,</font>

449
00:27:18,398 --> 00:27:20,128
<font color=#FFFF00>so you are working...</font>

450
00:27:20,598 --> 00:27:21,768
<font color=#FFFF00>and writing every day.</font>

451
00:27:21,998 --> 00:27:24,368
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't dress up and hang out with your friends.</font>

452
00:27:28,398 --> 00:27:29,398
<font color=#FFFF00>It breaks my heart...</font>

453
00:27:30,398 --> 00:27:31,868
<font color=#FFFF00>to see you working.</font>

454
00:27:33,598 --> 00:27:34,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't say that, Grandma.</font>

455
00:27:35,298 --> 00:27:37,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm really happy now.</font>

456
00:27:43,728 --> 00:27:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandma, why are you crying?</font>

457
00:27:56,628 --> 00:27:58,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is she?</font>

458
00:28:00,298 --> 00:28:01,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh.</font>

459
00:28:03,928 --> 00:28:05,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh.</font>

460
00:28:07,028 --> 00:28:09,898
<font color=#FFFF00>How longer should Dong Hui wait?</font>

461
00:28:10,428 --> 00:28:12,968
<font color=#FFFF00>She turned 27 already.</font>

462
00:28:13,568 --> 00:28:17,498
<font color=#FFFF00>You really have to do something with her now.</font>

463
00:28:18,198 --> 00:28:19,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Please wait a little longer.</font>

464
00:28:20,298 --> 00:28:21,668
<font color=#FFFF00>It's almost done.</font>

465
00:28:22,398 --> 00:28:24,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Please hurry up.</font>

466
00:28:25,298 --> 00:28:28,398
<font color=#FFFF00>You know my days are numbered.</font>

467
00:28:29,168 --> 00:28:30,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you not going to sleep?</font>

468
00:28:31,428 --> 00:28:33,228
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing here?</font>

469
00:28:33,228 --> 00:28:34,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing.</font>

470
00:28:34,498 --> 00:28:35,928
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean it's nothing?</font>

471
00:28:36,268 --> 00:28:39,298
<font color=#FFFF00>- Never mind. - You really smell fishy.</font>

472
00:28:39,298 --> 00:28:41,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh, do you have a boyfriend?</font>

473
00:28:45,968 --> 00:28:46,998
<font color=#FFFF00>That night,</font>

474
00:28:47,498 --> 00:28:49,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I went to Han River...</font>

475
00:28:49,928 --> 00:28:51,428
<font color=#FFFF00>to do some night fishing.</font>

476
00:28:52,268 --> 00:28:54,498
<font color=#FFFF00>On the way, I saw a crying boy.</font>

477
00:28:54,768 --> 00:28:56,468
<font color=#FFFF00>He was crying so hard.</font>

478
00:28:56,468 --> 00:28:57,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

479
00:28:57,698 --> 00:29:00,168
<font color=#FFFF00>- He was wearing only a thin jacket. - Hyun Woo!</font>

480
00:29:00,168 --> 00:29:03,068
<font color=#FFFF00>He was wearing shoes, but he wasn't wearing any socks.</font>

481
00:29:04,398 --> 00:29:07,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

482
00:29:14,068 --> 00:29:15,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Sir.</font>

483
00:29:15,728 --> 00:29:18,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you get any calls from the police?</font>

484
00:29:19,128 --> 00:29:21,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry, but none yet.</font>

485
00:29:43,668 --> 00:29:46,128
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't do that.</font>

486
00:29:46,198 --> 00:29:48,228
<font color=#FFFF00>- You will get scolded. - Really?</font>

487
00:30:00,668 --> 00:30:02,768
<font color=#FFFF00>You should be busy preparing for your wedding.</font>

488
00:30:02,798 --> 00:30:04,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you keep calling me?</font>

489
00:30:04,468 --> 00:30:07,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you ask your boyfriend about Golden Street?</font>

490
00:30:07,598 --> 00:30:09,098
<font color=#FFFF00>It's true, isn't it?</font>

491
00:30:09,298 --> 00:30:12,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Never mind. I am not going to ask him.</font>

492
00:30:12,568 --> 00:30:14,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure he had his reasons.</font>

493
00:30:14,698 --> 00:30:16,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you keep denying that it's him?</font>

494
00:30:17,228 --> 00:30:20,968
<font color=#FFFF00>David Lee is still the CEO of Golden Street.</font>

495
00:30:21,598 --> 00:30:24,268
<font color=#FFFF00>- When I went there the other day... - Seon Hwa.</font>

496
00:30:24,868 --> 00:30:26,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Maybe he's afraid that...</font>

497
00:30:26,468 --> 00:30:28,868
<font color=#FFFF00>once girls find out that he's super rich...</font>

498
00:30:28,868 --> 00:30:32,068
<font color=#FFFF00>they won't love him sincerely.</font>

499
00:30:32,728 --> 00:30:33,728
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

500
00:30:34,268 --> 00:30:36,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be killing 2 birds with 1 stone if that's the case.</font>

501
00:30:36,728 --> 00:30:38,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I will pretend I'm sincerely in love with him,</font>

502
00:30:38,598 --> 00:30:41,328
<font color=#FFFF00>and later when I find out that he's rich, I will get rich too.</font>

503
00:30:41,568 --> 00:30:44,268
<font color=#FFFF00>How nice would it be? Right?</font>

504
00:30:45,568 --> 00:30:46,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Good luck with your wedding.</font>

505
00:30:52,228 --> 00:30:55,628
<font color=#FFFF00>How can they be so selfish and think about only their interests?</font>

506
00:30:55,728 --> 00:30:57,598
<font color=#FFFF00>This is just way over the line.</font>

507
00:30:59,398 --> 00:31:01,328
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the Contents Department of FGC.</font>

508
00:31:01,368 --> 00:31:04,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I called to find out when Writer Kim's contract will be over.</font>

509
00:31:04,698 --> 00:31:07,798
<font color=#FFFF00>You have a lot of other writers.</font>

510
00:31:08,768 --> 00:31:11,068
<font color=#FFFF00>We're asking you to release one writer early.</font>

511
00:31:11,468 --> 00:31:13,268
<font color=#FFFF00>She's not even assigned to any project yet.</font>

512
00:31:14,768 --> 00:31:17,628
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not that we don't want to go there.</font>

513
00:31:17,728 --> 00:31:21,468
<font color=#FFFF00>We have an emergency here, so we're asking to delay the meeting.</font>

514
00:31:22,498 --> 00:31:24,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Can we have a meeting, please?</font>

515
00:31:26,228 --> 00:31:29,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I will call you back.</font>

516
00:31:35,468 --> 00:31:38,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I appreciate the Marketing Team for helping us out.</font>

517
00:31:38,898 --> 00:31:42,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Thanks to Director Bang, we didn't lose the airing right.</font>

518
00:31:43,498 --> 00:31:45,168
<font color=#FFFF00>As long as we find a writer and a project,</font>

519
00:31:45,198 --> 00:31:46,468
<font color=#FFFF00>everything will go as planned.</font>

520
00:31:46,768 --> 00:31:48,028
<font color=#FFFF00>So don't be too disheartened.</font>

521
00:31:48,498 --> 00:31:50,268
<font color=#FFFF00>This crisis...</font>

522
00:31:50,598 --> 00:31:52,328
<font color=#FFFF00>might turn into a better opportunity.</font>

523
00:31:52,398 --> 00:31:55,328
<font color=#FFFF00>As you must know, the Contents Marketing Department...</font>

524
00:31:55,598 --> 00:31:58,368
<font color=#FFFF00>will be removed if anything goes wrong.</font>

525
00:32:00,028 --> 00:32:01,868
<font color=#FFFF00>The general shareholders' meeting will be held soon.</font>

526
00:32:01,998 --> 00:32:06,128
<font color=#FFFF00>That meeting will determine the fate of this department.</font>

527
00:32:06,368 --> 00:32:10,228
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I will never waste this last chance.</font>

528
00:32:10,568 --> 00:32:11,998
<font color=#FFFF00>It's for all of us.</font>

529
00:32:13,398 --> 00:32:15,828
<font color=#FFFF00>This is our last chance.</font>

530
00:32:17,098 --> 00:32:18,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's make it work.</font>

531
00:32:18,798 --> 00:32:20,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes. - Okay.</font>

532
00:32:21,468 --> 00:32:23,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Producer Kim, please distribute those.</font>

533
00:32:23,668 --> 00:32:24,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

534
00:32:33,068 --> 00:32:36,468
<font color=#FFFF00>These are the scripts we've been collecting.</font>

535
00:32:36,768 --> 00:32:39,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Please read them thoroughly and choose good ones.</font>

536
00:32:39,498 --> 00:32:43,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I've collected the scripts of both experienced and new writers.</font>

537
00:32:43,668 --> 00:32:46,998
<font color=#FFFF00>To make the selection process as fair as possible,</font>

538
00:32:47,198 --> 00:32:48,998
<font color=#FFFF00>we have eliminated the names of the writers.</font>

539
00:32:49,068 --> 00:32:52,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't it better to go with an experienced writer's script?</font>

540
00:32:53,328 --> 00:32:56,968
<font color=#FFFF00>It's easier for us to do business if the writer is experienced.</font>

541
00:32:57,168 --> 00:33:01,128
<font color=#FFFF00>When we analyze the trend of successful replacement programs,</font>

542
00:33:01,298 --> 00:33:04,198
<font color=#FFFF00>we can see that the programs reviewed as being new and...</font>

543
00:33:04,468 --> 00:33:08,168
<font color=#FFFF00>original and received higher ratings were...</font>

544
00:33:08,228 --> 00:33:10,728
<font color=#FFFF00>often the works of new writers.</font>

545
00:33:10,998 --> 00:33:13,728
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. Please read them by tomorrow,</font>

546
00:33:13,798 --> 00:33:15,368
<font color=#FFFF00>and we will talk again.</font>

547
00:33:16,268 --> 00:33:18,698
<font color=#FFFF00>- By tomorrow? - Please do.</font>

548
00:33:48,568 --> 00:33:49,698
<font color=#FFFF00>You're late.</font>

549
00:33:50,398 --> 00:33:53,068
<font color=#FFFF00>- What now? - Seong Joon.</font>

550
00:33:54,168 --> 00:33:55,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Can we talk?</font>

551
00:34:13,698 --> 00:34:16,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you upset that I brought you here without asking permission?</font>

552
00:34:18,268 --> 00:34:19,498
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

553
00:34:22,028 --> 00:34:25,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I felt bad for making you pay last time.</font>

554
00:34:27,068 --> 00:34:28,498
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't have to feel bad.</font>

555
00:34:34,338 --> 00:34:36,798
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it that you want to tell me?</font>

556
00:34:41,598 --> 00:34:43,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I have something to ask.</font>

557
00:34:45,768 --> 00:34:49,128
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard you were adopted when you were very little.</font>

558
00:34:52,398 --> 00:34:55,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I was wondering if you remembered anything before you were adopted.</font>

559
00:34:56,468 --> 00:34:59,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- Please stop. - Do you remember where you lived?</font>

560
00:34:59,728 --> 00:35:00,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Or do you remember your father?</font>

561
00:35:03,338 --> 00:35:04,338
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

562
00:35:05,228 --> 00:35:06,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you remember your brother?</font>

563
00:35:08,838 --> 00:35:11,838
<font color=#FFFF00>- What are you doing? - Please don't be upset.</font>

564
00:35:12,468 --> 00:35:15,168
<font color=#FFFF00>If you remember anything, please tell me.</font>

565
00:35:15,838 --> 00:35:16,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I beg you.</font>

566
00:35:25,338 --> 00:35:26,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

567
00:35:28,598 --> 00:35:29,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Who are you?</font>

568
00:35:30,338 --> 00:35:32,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you going after me?</font>

569
00:35:33,728 --> 00:35:34,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon,</font>

570
00:35:35,398 --> 00:35:37,268
<font color=#FFFF00>please calm down and listen to me.</font>

571
00:35:37,268 --> 00:35:40,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Who are you? Why are you so interested in my family?</font>

572
00:35:40,998 --> 00:35:43,198
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Joon. - I warned you.</font>

573
00:35:43,568 --> 00:35:45,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to meddle with my family!</font>

574
00:35:48,298 --> 00:35:50,428
<font color=#FFFF00>What is he doing?</font>

575
00:35:51,368 --> 00:35:52,698
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Mr. Lee.</font>

576
00:35:53,098 --> 00:35:55,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, what are you doing?</font>

577
00:35:57,128 --> 00:35:58,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Leave him alone!</font>

578
00:35:58,838 --> 00:36:00,838
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad. - What are you doing?</font>

579
00:36:03,228 --> 00:36:04,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you all right, Mr. Lee?</font>

580
00:36:10,398 --> 00:36:13,228
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on, Boy?</font>

581
00:36:14,968 --> 00:36:15,968
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

582
00:36:16,568 --> 00:36:18,628
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's my fault. - Dad,</font>

583
00:36:19,968 --> 00:36:21,068
<font color=#FFFF00>let's go home.</font>

584
00:36:22,128 --> 00:36:23,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go home.</font>

585
00:36:58,928 --> 00:37:00,498
<font color=#FFFF00>(Scene 8, Ji Won's House)</font>

586
00:37:22,338 --> 00:37:23,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Were you writing?</font>

587
00:37:25,068 --> 00:37:26,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

588
00:37:27,568 --> 00:37:30,368
<font color=#FFFF00>It's cold outside. Can I come in?</font>

589
00:37:33,968 --> 00:37:35,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Today's been a long day for me.</font>

590
00:37:37,568 --> 00:37:40,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Please give me a warm cup of tea.</font>

591
00:37:42,898 --> 00:37:45,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait here. I will go outside.</font>

592
00:38:01,468 --> 00:38:02,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Is something wrong?</font>

593
00:38:03,838 --> 00:38:05,628
<font color=#FFFF00>No, nothing is wrong.</font>

594
00:38:07,068 --> 00:38:09,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Well then.</font>

595
00:38:13,128 --> 00:38:14,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Here.</font>

596
00:38:15,228 --> 00:38:16,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Everyone is reading these.</font>

597
00:38:17,598 --> 00:38:20,268
<font color=#FFFF00>You should read them...</font>

598
00:38:20,428 --> 00:38:22,298
<font color=#FFFF00>and see which one is good.</font>

599
00:38:24,398 --> 00:38:26,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it okay for me to read them?</font>

600
00:38:26,898 --> 00:38:28,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I trust your judgement.</font>

601
00:38:31,198 --> 00:38:33,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I will read them.</font>

602
00:38:36,428 --> 00:38:38,628
<font color=#FFFF00>It's late. You should go down now.</font>

603
00:38:39,968 --> 00:38:43,028
<font color=#FFFF00>You should go down now. The elders are expecting you.</font>

604
00:38:44,568 --> 00:38:45,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

605
00:38:46,338 --> 00:38:48,198
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you today?</font>

606
00:38:49,728 --> 00:38:51,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Since you brought it up...</font>

607
00:38:54,128 --> 00:38:57,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it would be better if you don't come up here from now on.</font>

608
00:38:58,128 --> 00:39:01,628
<font color=#FFFF00>- Why? - You must be tired from work.</font>

609
00:39:02,668 --> 00:39:04,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I will write on my own from now on.</font>

610
00:39:07,798 --> 00:39:09,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Something happened, right?</font>

611
00:39:10,338 --> 00:39:13,168
<font color=#FFFF00>No, nothing happened. It's just...</font>

612
00:39:13,868 --> 00:39:15,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I think I didn't think about...</font>

613
00:39:15,698 --> 00:39:19,268
<font color=#FFFF00>your situation because I was only thinking about myself.</font>

614
00:39:20,068 --> 00:39:23,198
<font color=#FFFF00>You must have a lot of things to do besides teaching me at night.</font>

615
00:39:24,728 --> 00:39:25,798
<font color=#FFFF00>That's...</font>

616
00:39:26,498 --> 00:39:27,838
<font color=#FFFF00>my favorite thing to do.</font>

617
00:39:29,298 --> 00:39:30,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Teaching you.</font>

618
00:39:41,968 --> 00:39:42,968
<font color=#FFFF00>But still,</font>

619
00:39:44,128 --> 00:39:46,028
<font color=#FFFF00>please don't come here anymore.</font>

