00:40:11,568 --> 00:40:13,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

623
00:40:13,668 --> 00:40:15,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

624
00:40:16,098 --> 00:40:18,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

625
00:40:19,398 --> 00:40:22,728
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sang Woo. - Hyun Woo!</font>

626
00:40:22,838 --> 00:40:24,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Sang Woo!</font>

627
00:40:37,098 --> 00:40:38,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir?</font>

628
00:40:48,168 --> 00:40:50,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you all right, Sir?</font>

629
00:40:53,268 --> 00:40:55,368
<font color=#FFFF00>You drank a lot last night.</font>

630
00:40:56,198 --> 00:40:57,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I did.</font>

631
00:40:57,838 --> 00:40:58,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I did drink a bit.</font>

632
00:40:59,368 --> 00:41:00,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you meet Seong Joon?</font>

633
00:41:02,768 --> 00:41:03,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I did.</font>

634
00:41:03,898 --> 00:41:05,928
<font color=#FFFF00>You need to get a hold of yourself, especially in times like this.</font>

635
00:41:06,028 --> 00:41:07,798
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you meet him?</font>

636
00:41:09,368 --> 00:41:11,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew it was a mistake.</font>

637
00:41:13,198 --> 00:41:15,798
<font color=#FFFF00>But I couldn't stand it. I was so anxious.</font>

638
00:41:16,198 --> 00:41:17,598
<font color=#FFFF00>You were too hasty.</font>

639
00:41:17,838 --> 00:41:20,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Then what do you think I should do?</font>

640
00:41:21,028 --> 00:41:22,338
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm about to lose my mind.</font>

641
00:41:22,628 --> 00:41:25,268
<font color=#FFFF00>He grabbed me by the collar and despises me,</font>

642
00:41:25,768 --> 00:41:27,198
<font color=#FFFF00>and he might be my brother.</font>

643
00:41:27,498 --> 00:41:29,368
<font color=#FFFF00>What am I supposed I do?</font>

644
00:41:36,428 --> 00:41:37,498
<font color=#FFFF00>You should go.</font>

645
00:41:38,198 --> 00:41:39,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be in here.</font>

646
00:41:46,398 --> 00:41:47,428
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness.</font>

647
00:41:48,368 --> 00:41:49,398
<font color=#FFFF00>You're here.</font>

648
00:41:49,468 --> 00:41:52,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope I am not intruding.</font>

649
00:41:52,168 --> 00:41:53,628
<font color=#FFFF00>You are not.</font>

650
00:41:53,868 --> 00:41:55,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I was about to have some coffee.</font>

651
00:41:56,028 --> 00:41:57,228
<font color=#FFFF00>- Were you? - Yes.</font>

652
00:41:57,398 --> 00:41:59,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Could I join you then?</font>

653
00:41:59,838 --> 00:42:02,498
<font color=#FFFF00>- Of course. Please wait. - Okay.</font>

654
00:42:16,028 --> 00:42:18,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know why he did...</font>

655
00:42:18,768 --> 00:42:22,768
<font color=#FFFF00>such a thing to you last night.</font>

656
00:42:23,998 --> 00:42:26,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you can be understanding and forgive him.</font>

657
00:42:27,228 --> 00:42:29,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I asked him why he did it,</font>

658
00:42:29,868 --> 00:42:31,698
<font color=#FFFF00>but he didn't say anything.</font>

659
00:42:32,868 --> 00:42:35,268
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it was my fault.</font>

660
00:42:35,498 --> 00:42:38,498
<font color=#FFFF00>It's very unlike him.</font>

661
00:42:38,498 --> 00:42:40,068
<font color=#FFFF00>He's very kind.</font>

662
00:42:40,668 --> 00:42:42,198
<font color=#FFFF00>He was...</font>

663
00:42:42,428 --> 00:42:45,598
<font color=#FFFF00>so different from his brothers ever since he was young.</font>

664
00:42:46,128 --> 00:42:49,228
<font color=#FFFF00>He is considerate and thoughtful.</font>

665
00:42:49,228 --> 00:42:51,068
<font color=#FFFF00>He is mature too.</font>

666
00:42:52,868 --> 00:42:53,998
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like...</font>

667
00:42:54,838 --> 00:42:57,228
<font color=#FFFF00>he's the oldest son.</font>

668
00:42:57,798 --> 00:42:59,728
<font color=#FFFF00>You saw him the other day.</font>

669
00:42:59,928 --> 00:43:02,968
<font color=#FFFF00>He didn't go out even on a holiday...</font>

670
00:43:03,068 --> 00:43:05,498
<font color=#FFFF00>so that he could play go with his father.</font>

671
00:43:07,428 --> 00:43:10,498
<font color=#FFFF00>When he was about eight years old,</font>

672
00:43:10,928 --> 00:43:12,498
<font color=#FFFF00>he didn't go out...</font>

673
00:43:12,928 --> 00:43:15,268
<font color=#FFFF00>and always hover around me.</font>

674
00:43:16,098 --> 00:43:18,798
<font color=#FFFF00>So I taught him how to play go.</font>

675
00:43:20,268 --> 00:43:21,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that so?</font>

676
00:43:21,498 --> 00:43:25,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I could only win against him until he was 12 years old.</font>

677
00:43:25,668 --> 00:43:27,968
<font color=#FFFF00>After that, I kept losing.</font>

678
00:43:28,028 --> 00:43:29,868
<font color=#FFFF00>That's how smart he is.</font>

679
00:43:32,198 --> 00:43:34,338
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess he is smart indeed.</font>

680
00:43:34,698 --> 00:43:38,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I really like him a lot.</font>

681
00:43:38,628 --> 00:43:39,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Parental love is...</font>

682
00:43:40,228 --> 00:43:42,368
<font color=#FFFF00>one-sided, isn't it?</font>

683
00:43:44,728 --> 00:43:46,068
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why...</font>

684
00:43:47,928 --> 00:43:50,128
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd like you to give you this Korean traditional sweets and cookies.</font>

685
00:43:50,428 --> 00:43:52,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I received it over the holidays. It's quite expensive.</font>

686
00:43:52,168 --> 00:43:54,228
<font color=#FFFF00>It goes well with coffee.</font>

687
00:43:54,698 --> 00:43:57,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't. There's no need, Sir.</font>

688
00:43:57,728 --> 00:43:59,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Please accept it.</font>

689
00:43:59,628 --> 00:44:02,928
<font color=#FFFF00>This is all for my son.</font>

690
00:44:04,668 --> 00:44:08,228
<font color=#FFFF00>He would never do anything like it.</font>

691
00:44:08,728 --> 00:44:12,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I think he must be under a lot of stress at work.</font>

692
00:44:13,498 --> 00:44:16,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Please forgive him this one time.</font>

693
00:44:25,398 --> 00:44:26,428
<font color=#FFFF00>This is delicious.</font>

694
00:44:28,068 --> 00:44:29,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you teasing me?</font>

695
00:44:30,468 --> 00:44:33,368
<font color=#FFFF00>All we need to do is check the fact.</font>

696
00:44:33,598 --> 00:44:36,668
<font color=#FFFF00>The police has to officially check just one line.</font>

697
00:44:37,598 --> 00:44:39,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Your hard working of 23 years is about to be...</font>

698
00:44:40,498 --> 00:44:43,198
<font color=#FFFF00>summarized into one sentence.</font>

699
00:44:45,228 --> 00:44:47,128
<font color=#FFFF00>I know waiting can be difficult.</font>

700
00:44:47,968 --> 00:44:51,698
<font color=#FFFF00>How about doing something else while you wait for it?</font>

701
00:44:53,498 --> 00:44:54,828
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

702
00:44:55,398 --> 00:44:57,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm talking about Jeong Eun.</font>

703
00:44:57,698 --> 00:45:01,728
<font color=#FFFF00>To you, she is just as important as Seong Joon.</font>

704
00:45:01,968 --> 00:45:03,068
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you implying?</font>

705
00:45:04,498 --> 00:45:05,998
<font color=#FFFF00>She's the only person...</font>

706
00:45:06,398 --> 00:45:08,728
<font color=#FFFF00>who trusts and waits for you...</font>

707
00:45:08,728 --> 00:45:10,468
<font color=#FFFF00>even though you're not her family.</font>

708
00:45:11,128 --> 00:45:13,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Whether you admit or not,</font>

709
00:45:13,498 --> 00:45:15,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I believe I am right.</font>

710
00:45:16,728 --> 00:45:17,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Have some.</font>

711
00:45:19,198 --> 00:45:20,598
<font color=#FFFF00>This is good.</font>

712
00:45:29,628 --> 00:45:30,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

713
00:45:30,998 --> 00:45:32,598
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you?</font>

714
00:45:33,028 --> 00:45:34,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really have to ask?</font>

715
00:45:37,028 --> 00:45:39,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you still mad at me?</font>

716
00:45:40,228 --> 00:45:42,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't mind me. Just keep going where you were headed.</font>

717
00:45:43,398 --> 00:45:44,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

718
00:45:44,798 --> 00:45:47,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop drinking. Please?</font>

719
00:45:48,898 --> 00:45:52,168
<font color=#FFFF00>You told me to stay out of your life. Why are you butting in mine?</font>

720
00:45:53,028 --> 00:45:56,268
<font color=#FFFF00>It looks like you are going on a date with that guy.</font>

721
00:45:56,428 --> 00:45:58,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't be impatient. Just go.</font>

722
00:45:58,968 --> 00:46:01,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't get involved in your life.</font>

723
00:46:02,128 --> 00:46:03,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Children don't listen to their parents.</font>

724
00:46:04,398 --> 00:46:06,828
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to fight with you, Mom.</font>

725
00:46:08,098 --> 00:46:12,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't think you are all alone and you are lonely.</font>

726
00:46:12,328 --> 00:46:14,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't we get along?</font>

727
00:46:14,668 --> 00:46:16,998
<font color=#FFFF00>All we have in this world is each other.</font>

728
00:46:18,898 --> 00:46:22,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Since you've been dating, it sounds like you know everything.</font>

729
00:46:23,828 --> 00:46:24,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Fine.</font>

730
00:46:25,198 --> 00:46:27,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me see how long that will last.</font>

731
00:46:29,028 --> 00:46:30,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Love?</font>

732
00:46:31,298 --> 00:46:32,968
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

733
00:46:33,498 --> 00:46:36,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think I was in love once?</font>

734
00:46:37,998 --> 00:46:39,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

735
00:46:40,068 --> 00:46:41,128
<font color=#FFFF00>You.</font>

736
00:46:41,698 --> 00:46:43,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo started learning to be an opera singer. Did you know?</font>

737
00:46:43,828 --> 00:46:44,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

738
00:46:45,098 --> 00:46:46,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

739
00:46:46,198 --> 00:46:49,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo is learning to be an opera singer.</font>

740
00:46:51,198 --> 00:46:52,368
<font color=#FFFF00>It's funny.</font>

741
00:46:52,928 --> 00:46:55,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I avoided singers all my life.</font>

742
00:46:56,928 --> 00:46:59,968
<font color=#FFFF00>There's another man who sings in our family.</font>

743
00:47:02,298 --> 00:47:03,468
<font color=#FFFF00>By the look of it,</font>

744
00:47:04,168 --> 00:47:06,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't be able to avoid men who sing.</font>

745
00:47:09,628 --> 00:47:11,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Does it remind you about Dad?</font>

746
00:47:12,328 --> 00:47:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it doesn't.</font>

747
00:47:16,328 --> 00:47:17,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Go now.</font>

748
00:47:19,568 --> 00:47:21,768
<font color=#FFFF00>You should live your own life.</font>

749
00:47:21,768 --> 00:47:23,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry about me.</font>

750
00:47:25,998 --> 00:47:27,268
<font color=#FFFF00>What? Music?</font>

751
00:47:27,368 --> 00:47:28,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

752
00:47:29,428 --> 00:47:31,898
<font color=#FFFF00>What have you been doing lately?</font>

753
00:47:32,268 --> 00:47:35,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo is about to be an amazing opera singer,</font>

754
00:47:35,198 --> 00:47:37,428
<font color=#FFFF00>but you are not even interested in your own son.</font>

755
00:47:37,428 --> 00:47:38,698
<font color=#FFFF00>You come home late all the time now.</font>

756
00:47:38,898 --> 00:47:40,668
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you do this to me?</font>

757
00:47:43,128 --> 00:47:44,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know...</font>

758
00:47:44,368 --> 00:47:46,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo had a talent for singing.</font>

759
00:47:46,628 --> 00:47:49,128
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey. - I'm busy too.</font>

760
00:47:49,498 --> 00:47:51,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know how much work I have?</font>

761
00:47:51,898 --> 00:47:54,328
<font color=#FFFF00>To put it bluntly, if he wants to become an opera singer,</font>

762
00:47:54,598 --> 00:47:57,428
<font color=#FFFF00>who's going to pay for all those lessons? Are you going to pay?</font>

763
00:47:58,128 --> 00:48:00,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to pay them eventually.</font>

764
00:48:00,698 --> 00:48:03,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Then I must go out and work. Should I just stay at home?</font>

765
00:48:03,868 --> 00:48:06,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey. In times like this,</font>

766
00:48:06,498 --> 00:48:09,898
<font color=#FFFF00>we have to separate our jobs more clearly.</font>

767
00:48:09,998 --> 00:48:12,228
<font color=#FFFF00>You are in charge of our son's education.</font>

768
00:48:12,398 --> 00:48:14,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I am in charge of making a lot of money...</font>

769
00:48:14,198 --> 00:48:16,568
<font color=#FFFF00>so that we can raise Chang Soo well.</font>

770
00:48:16,568 --> 00:48:19,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I should also expand my influence.</font>

771
00:48:20,028 --> 00:48:22,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Mark my words. I will do my best...</font>

772
00:48:22,428 --> 00:48:24,298
<font color=#FFFF00>so that Chang Soo can sing the...</font>

773
00:48:24,628 --> 00:48:28,068
<font color=#FFFF00>national anthem at the President's inauguration after 10 years.</font>

774
00:48:30,028 --> 00:48:31,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to the gym.</font>

775
00:48:32,268 --> 00:48:33,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey. Where are you going?</font>

776
00:48:34,298 --> 00:48:35,868
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey. - Hold on.</font>

777
00:48:58,198 --> 00:48:59,268
<font color=#FFFF00>What was that just now?</font>

778
00:48:59,828 --> 00:49:02,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Doesn't he know that having small muscles is in trend now?</font>

779
00:49:11,098 --> 00:49:13,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Han. Here.</font>

780
00:49:31,368 --> 00:49:35,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you so late? I was waiting for you.</font>

781
00:49:39,468 --> 00:49:40,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, I'm sorry.</font>

782
00:49:41,728 --> 00:49:43,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you finished with exercising?</font>

783
00:49:43,568 --> 00:49:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>No, I'm a work out buff.</font>

784
00:49:46,168 --> 00:49:47,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I haven't done far from enough.</font>

785
00:49:47,898 --> 00:49:50,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll move to that area. Please follow me.</font>

786
00:49:50,798 --> 00:49:52,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

787
00:50:04,428 --> 00:50:06,928
<font color=#FFFF00>You should pull it like this.</font>

788
00:50:06,968 --> 00:50:08,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Please keep up.</font>

789
00:50:10,398 --> 00:50:12,428
<font color=#FFFF00>You're unbelievably weak.</font>

790
00:50:12,898 --> 00:50:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness.</font>

791
00:50:24,168 --> 00:50:26,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- Try it again. - Okay.</font>

792
00:50:39,698 --> 00:50:40,968
<font color=#FFFF00>What's all this?</font>

793
00:50:41,098 --> 00:50:42,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't you see them?</font>

794
00:50:42,898 --> 00:50:46,598
<font color=#FFFF00>These are a CD, a book of opera scores, and an opera textbook.</font>

795
00:50:46,898 --> 00:50:49,598
<font color=#FFFF00>These are autobiographies of great opera singers.</font>

796
00:50:49,668 --> 00:50:52,668
<font color=#FFFF00>And these are English and math workbooks for Ji Hoon.</font>

797
00:50:53,468 --> 00:50:55,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you giving these to me?</font>

798
00:50:55,168 --> 00:50:58,268
<font color=#FFFF00>You should become a good mother too.</font>

799
00:50:58,668 --> 00:51:01,068
<font color=#FFFF00>You should thank me.</font>

800
00:51:01,228 --> 00:51:02,968
<font color=#FFFF00>If it weren't for me,</font>

801
00:51:03,068 --> 00:51:05,568
<font color=#FFFF00>you would have never been able to discover Chang Soo's talent.</font>

802
00:51:06,098 --> 00:51:09,128
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't even had time to visit your kids' schools.</font>

803
00:51:09,168 --> 00:51:11,728
<font color=#FFFF00>- You still don't have time, right? - So what?</font>

804
00:51:12,068 --> 00:51:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be even busier because of Chang Soo.</font>

805
00:51:14,998 --> 00:51:19,068
<font color=#FFFF00>It's crucial to find a good instructor.</font>

806
00:51:19,298 --> 00:51:22,698
<font color=#FFFF00>What about Professor Park you met the other day?</font>

807
00:51:22,728 --> 00:51:26,128
<font color=#FFFF00>It's illegal to receive lessons from college professors.</font>

808
00:51:27,268 --> 00:51:28,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

809
00:51:28,428 --> 00:51:31,228
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not easy to find a good teacher.</font>

810
00:51:31,928 --> 00:51:35,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Although I know nothing about classical music,</font>

811
00:51:35,628 --> 00:51:38,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I will find the best teacher for Chang Soo by any means...</font>

812
00:51:39,098 --> 00:51:43,098
<font color=#FFFF00>with the skills I've earned when I took care of Ji Hoon.</font>

813
00:51:43,298 --> 00:51:46,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- How will you do that? - I already contacted some.</font>

814
00:51:48,298 --> 00:51:49,928
<font color=#FFFF00>You're really amazing.</font>

815
00:51:51,328 --> 00:51:54,028
<font color=#FFFF00>So I need you to listen to this CD...</font>

816
00:51:54,028 --> 00:51:55,898
<font color=#FFFF00>and study opera music...</font>

817
00:51:55,968 --> 00:51:59,068
<font color=#FFFF00>while I am away.</font>

818
00:51:59,268 --> 00:52:02,368
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hee Sook, I... - Don't you want...</font>

819
00:52:02,398 --> 00:52:04,598
<font color=#FFFF00>to raise Chang Soo into a great opera singer?</font>

820
00:52:06,398 --> 00:52:08,798
<font color=#FFFF00>- Fine. - And...</font>

821
00:52:09,428 --> 00:52:11,628
<font color=#FFFF00>you also need to take care of your own son,</font>

822
00:52:11,628 --> 00:52:13,468
<font color=#FFFF00>not just other's son.</font>

823
00:52:15,498 --> 00:52:19,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell Ji Hoon to finish these in a week and bring them to me.</font>

824
00:52:19,998 --> 00:52:22,298
