942
01:00:16,698 --> 01:00:19,798
<font color=#FFFF00>You cook well, you handle logs well,</font>

943
01:00:19,928 --> 01:00:21,268
<font color=#FFFF00>you make fire well,</font>

944
01:00:21,998 --> 01:00:23,898
<font color=#FFFF00>and you listen to my song well.</font>

945
01:00:25,728 --> 01:00:27,828
<font color=#FFFF00>I've had such a hard time...</font>

946
01:00:28,068 --> 01:00:29,628
